===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''leather'''

#A tough material produced from the [[skin]] of [[animal]]s, by [[tan#Verb|tanning]] or similar process, used e.g. for [[clothing]].
#A piece of leather used for [[polish#Verb|polishing]].
#(''colloquialism'') A [[cricket]] ball or [[football]].
#(''plural'': '''leathers''') Leather clothing, often worn by [[motorcycle]] riders.
#{{baseball}} A good defensive play
#: ''Jones showed good leather to snare that [[liner]].''

